  Tok8-tok8 Ki-tok Oe7 Ka7 Goa2 Tam-tng. 
  Kou2-cha2 kau3 taN e5 toa7 seng3-jin5 gau5 lang5, eng7 loa7 choe7 e5 sim-su, sou2 chhut-lat8 kang2-kiu3--e5 tok8-tok8 thian-to7 na7-tiaN7. Thian-to7 chiu7-si7 beh chhoa7 phou2 thiN-e7 e5 lang5 li7-khui se3-siok8, jip8 seng3, chhut si2 jip8 oah8, kong2 khah siong5-se3, si7 hou7 phou2 thiN-e7 e5 lang5 long2 oe7 siam2-pi7 te7-gek8 e5 kan-khou2, lai5 jip8 eng2 oah8 e5 mng5. Chit ho7 mng7-toe5 sit8-chai7 iau3-kin2, tui3 cha2 kau3 taN e5 seng3-hian5, be7 u7 oe7 oan5-choan5 kai2-koat e5 hoat-tou7, put-kou3 si7 peng5-siong5 khou2-khng3 choe3 ho2, keng2-kai3 choe3 phaiN2--e5 chiah-e5 khau2-thau5 sian7 na7-tiaN7. 
  Tok8-tok8 u7 Ia5-sou Ki-tok pang3-sak sin-khu kiu3 se3-kan, m7 na7 thoan5-to7, sit8-chai7 oe7-kiaN5 to7-li2, sou2-i2 Seng3-keng kong2, “Eng2-oan2 hok-khi3 e5 toe7-ki i2-keng khia7-chai7, se3-kan lang5 kui-oa2--i chiu7 ho2.” Koh kong2, “Toe7-ki chiu7-si7 Ia5-sou Ki-tok, si7 Siong7-te3 tek8-piat siat-lip8.” Se3-kan lang5 oe7 kui-oa2 sin3--I, chiu7 sim-lai7 u7 pa2-chhi5, koat-toan3 boe7 chhin-chhiuN7 chun5 phu5 ti7 toa7 hai2 e5 tiong-kan, bong5-bong5 biau2-biau2, m7 chai beh tui3 ta2-loh8 khi3. 
  Chong2-si7 kui-oa2 Ki-tok e5 nng7 ho7 kang-tiaN5 m7-thang m7 chai, (1) Keng3-hok8 Ki-tok. (2) Sun7-than3 Seng3 Sin5. In-ui7 Ki-tok siok8 ti7 goa7-phe5, Seng3 Sin5 siok8 ti7 lai7-sim. Siok8 goa7-poe5 i3-su3 chiu7-si7 kiu3 se3 siok8 choe7 e5 kong-lo5 Ki-tok choe3 chiaN5--i, lan2 seng5-sim kui-oa2 chiu7 thang hiong2-siu7 kiu3 siok8 e5 un-tian2, bian2 chit8 li5-si khiam3-eng7--lan2. Siok8 lai7-sim e5 i3-su3 chiu7-si7 kam2-hoa3 e5 khui3-lat8 Seng3 Sin5 chiang2-koan2--i, chong2-si7 sun7-than3 ui5-keh8 si7 chai7 ti7 lan2 lang5. Sou2-i2 Ki-tok e5 kong-lo5 bo5 in-ui7 lan2 e5 ho2 phaiN2 lai5 ke-thiN kiam2-chio2, na7-si7 Seng3 Sin5 e5 kam2-hoa3 u7 kong-hau7 a2 bo5, si7 khoaN3 hit lang5 e5 sun7-than3 ui5-keh8, ku7-choat8 seng5-siu7 lai5 tiaN7-tioh8. Sou2-i2 te3 Ki-tok e5 lang5 m7-thang kan-ta oa2-kho3 ka-ki7 e5 sim-heng7, ng3-bang7 kau3 kong-tek oan5-boan2 e5 jit8 oe7 phoe3 Ki-tok e5 kiu3 un. In-ui7 kiu3 un si7 tui3 Siong7-te3 e5 jin5-ai3, Ki-tok e5 chu5-pi chhut, m7 si7 se3-kan e5 kim gun5 sou2 oe7 boe2--tit, iah8 m7 si7 oa2-kho3 kong-tek sou2 oe7 choe3 chiaN5. Na7-si7 lang5 ka-ki7 phah-sng3 it-seng choe3 lang5 kiaN5 tai7-chi3 kin2-sin7, ng3-bang7 beh tit-tioh8 Siong7-te3 e5 koan3-kou3, si7 chin toa7 chho3-gou7. In-ui7 Siong7-te3 si7 oan5-choan5 bo5 lang5 oe7 pi2-tit ban7 hun7 e5 chit8 hun7, siat-su2 lang5 kek8 gau5 chiau3-kou3 ka-ki7 e5 sim-heng7 kiaN5 choe3, chiau3 lang5 khoaN3 si7 ho2, chong2-si7 chiau3 ThiN khoaN3 si7 iau2 bo5 kau3-giah8, sou2-i2 kong2 Ki-tok e5 kiu3 un koat-toan3 boe7 tui3 lang5 e5 kong-tek lai5 tit--tioh8, che si7 beng5. Tok8-tok8 se3-kan lang5 tioh8 tu5-khi3 ka-ki7 oa2-kho3 e5 liam7-thau5, piaN3 khang i e5 chhiu2, khiam-hu i e5 sim, phak ti7 Ki-tok e5 bin7-cheng5 kiu5 kong2, “Goa2 bo5 tek-heng7 bo5 chai5-leng5, sim-lai7 moa2-moa2 choe7-koa3, pun2 boe7 kham-tit hiong2-siu7 kiu3 siok8 e5 kong-lo5, chi2 u7 ng3-bang7 oa2-kho3 Ki-tok e5 chu5-pi lai5 choe3 goa2 leng5-hun5 e5 po2-hou7, kau3 si2 bo5 soah na7-tiaN7.” 
  SiuN7 TiaN7 I2-keng Bo5 Mia7. 
  Cha2 jit8 u7 chit8 chiah toa7 chun5 ho7 choe3 Lim5-tun, tui3 Eng-kok khi3 o3-kok, keng-ke3 Hoat-kok Pit-su7-kai hai2-oan tu2-tioh8 po3-thau5 hong, hai2-eng2 chin toa7, chun5 hian2-lai5 hian2-khi3, bo5 loa7 ku2 chun5-piN e5 thih-pan2 phah phaiN2, chui2 lau7-jip8 chhng-lai7, lang5-kheh toa7 loan7. Chun5-teng2 u7 tiau3 sam-pan2 chun5, si7 pi7-pan7 tu2-tioh8 gui5-hiam2 thang eng7. Tai7-kong chiu7 pang3 sam-pan2 loh8 chui2, chhoa7 cheng3 lang5-kheh loh8--khi3. Toa7 chun5--nih8 u7 chit8 e5 chun-kui3 hu7-jin5-lang5, siuN7 put-ko3 chit8 chiah sio2 chun5 phu5 ti7 toa7 hong-eng2 e5 tiong-kan, tek-khak m7 tat8 toa7 chun5 lai7 e5 un2-tang3, chiu7 m7 loh8 sam-pan2, cheng3 lang5-kheh pek i tioh8 koaN2-kin2 loh8. M7 thiaN. Tai7-kong ko3 chiuN2 choe3 in khi3. Bo5 loa7 ku2, chun5-lai7 chui2 chiam7-chiam7 moa2, khiam3 chhun3 goa7 koaiN5 chiu7 tim5. Chun-kui3 hu7-jin5-lang5 tioh8-kip, m7-ku2 khoaN3 sam-pan2 i2-keng khi3 li2 goa7 hng7, toa7 siaN kio3, he7 beh eng7 nng7 chheng kim-pong7 tap-sia7. Cheng3 lang5-kheh kah tai7-kong ko3 to3-tng2 khi3 kiu3. Tai7-kong kong2, “Ti5--lah, theng3-hau7 sam-pan2 oa2-chun5, chun5 i2-keng tim5--loh8-khi3-liau2, na7 bo5, chun5 khong7-khong7 hian2 bo5 tiaN7 bo5 tioh8, si3-bin7 eng2 hiah toa7, khip-lat8 hui-siong5 kiong5, lan2 koat-toan3 ko3 boe7 oa2. Teh kiaN hit-e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 bo5 tit-tioh8 kiu3, kiaN-liau2 lin2 tioh8 soa3 te3 i si2.” Koh tiap8-a2 ku2 khoaN3 toa7 chun5 chiam7-chiam7 tim5, chun-kui3 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 hou7 chui2 im--tioh8, chhin-chhiuN7 iau2-ku2 teh kiu5 kiu3. Cheng3 lang5 khoaN3-kiN3 chit ho7 chhiN-chham2 long2 kong2 i tng si5 m7 thiaN khou2-khng3, chiah tioh8 ka-ki7 gou7 liau2 siN3-mia7. 
  Ia5-sou Ki-tok si7 se3-kan lang5 e5 kiu3-seng chun5, pang3-sak chit-e5 i2-goa7, bo5 pat8 e5 tit kiu3 e5 ng3-bang7. Goan7 tai7-ke than3 cha2 hoe5-thau5, chiah oe7 thang chiuN7 kau3 peng5-an e5 sou2-chai7, na7 bo5, tek-khak chhin-chhiuN7 hit-e5 chun-kui3 hu7-jin5-lang5 sit-loh8 siN3-mia7, tim5-loh8 khou2-hai2 e5 tiong-kan, eng2-oan2 bo5 tit-tioh8 oah8 e5 ng3-bang7. 
  Mou5-kui2 e5 Ke3-chhek. 
  Cha2 jit8 u7 chit8 lang5 bang7 kiN3 khi3 iu5 te7-hu2, khoaN3-kiN3 kui2 ong5 che7 ti7 koaiN5-tai5 e5 teng2-bin7, si7-oe7 pai5-liat8 cho2-iu7, kui2-chut kang2 chheng ban7, gu5-thau5 be2-bin7, khoan2-sit m7 na7 chit8 khoan2. Kui2-ong5 che7 ti7 tai5-teng2, chhut siaN chit8 e7 kio3, cheng3 kui2-chut long2 tioh8 in3, giam2-jian5 hong5-te3 kau3 kim-loan5 tian7 chit8-iuN7. 
  Bang7-kiN3 e5 lang5 khoaN3-kiN3 chit ho7 keng2-hong2, tu2-tu2 teh ki5-koai3 e5 tiong-kan, hut-jian5 thiaN-kiN3 kui2-ong5 thoan5-chi2, kong2, “Pun2 tai7-ong5 chit tiap8 ai3 keng2 choan-chhe khi3 hoan7-kan iu2-hek8 ban7 lang5, cho7-chok tak8 hang7 e5 choe7-ok, hou7 lang5 li7-khui Thian-kok lai5 jip8 be5-lou7, te7-gek8 ke tit-tioh8 chit8 lang5, chiu7 lan2 ke chit8 e5 pang-chan7. Chi7-chui7 beh khi3? Kin2-kin2 chiuN7 tian7 lai5 chau3.” Liam5-piN u7 chit8 e5 kui2-chut khi2-sin chau3 kong2, “Jin5-sin5 bo5 chai5-tiau7, tit-tioh8 tai7-ong5 chhut beng7-leng7, goan7 chin7 sim-su khui3-lat8, lai5 po3 tai7-ong5 e5 sim.” Ong5 mng7, “Li2 u7 sim2-mih8 ho2 ke3-chhek?” In3 kong2, “Goa2 beh ka7 lang5 kong2, Thian-tong5 te7-gek8 si7 bong5-bong5 biau2-biau2 e5 su7, Siong7-te3 u7 iaN2 a2 bo5, koh khah boe7 pin5-sin3--tit, put-ju5 kip8-si5 than3 ki-hoe7 khoai3-lok8 khah ho2.” 
  Kui2-ong5 kong2, “Boe7 eng7--tit, bok8 u7 pun2, chui2 u7 goan5, lang5 e5 pun2-goan5 chiu7-si7 Siong7-te3, che si7 li2 sou2 boe7 siam2-pi7, soe3-han3 gin2-a2 ma7 oe7 chai, sui-jian5 phu5-phio3 hong3-tong7 e5 siau3-lian5, tng chiu2-chui3 e5 si5 kong2 goa2 m7-bat Siong7-te3. Kau3 ti7 mi5-cheng7 to2 loh8 bin5-chhng5, be7 bat bo5 ka-ki7 siuN7 thiN-toe7 tek-khak u7 chu2-chaiN2, iah8 beng5 ho2 phaiN2 tek-khak u7 po3-eng3, cha2 oaN3 tiaN7-tioh8 boe7 chau2-siam2. Na7 kau3 piN7-tang7 gui5-kip e5 si5, i e5 thian-liong5 koh khah oah8-tang7, siong5-siong5 u7 e5 kau3 hit si5 ki5-to2 ai kiu5. Koh Siong7-te3 e5 chu5-pi chhiong-moa2 thiN-toe7 lai7, hun7 lan2 bo5 hoat-tou7 thang chou2-chi2--i, bo5 lun7 lang5 hoan7 choe7 loa7 tang7, siat-su2 hoan2-hoe2 koe2-piN3, lau5 kui2 tiam2 bak8-sai2, ki5-kiu5 kui2-ku3 Ia5-sou, bo5 m7 tit-tioh8 sia3-bian2 choe7, kiu3 i kau3 Thian-tong5. Li2 iong2-kam2 o-lo2, chong2-si7 ke3-chhek boe7 kiaN5--tit” Kong2 soah, koh chit8 e5 kui2 chau3 kong2, “Goa2 beh khi3.” 
  Kui2-ong5 kong2, “Li2 u7 siaN2 ho2 hoat-sut8 thang hou7 lang5 li7-khui Siong7-te3, thoa i jip8 te7-gek8?” In3 kong2, “Goa2 beh eng7 ham5-hou5 e5 oe7 ka7 lang5 kong2, thiN-toe7 lai7 sit8-chai7 u7 chu2-chaiN2, m7-ku2 I seng3 koh chheng-khi3, kek8 oan3-hun7 phaiN2, se3-kan lang5 bo5 chit8 e5 oe7 kham-tit chhin-kun7, ho5-hong3 lan2 si7 choe7-ok chhim tang7 e5 lang5, thai2-tho2 oe7 kham-tit tit-tioh8 Seng3 chheng-khi3 e5 Siong7-te3 koan3-kou3? An2-ni lang5 kap Siong7-te3 pun-khui, un2-tang3 jip8 ti7 tai7-ong5 e5 hoan7-ui5 lai7.” Kui2-ong5 kong2, “Chit ho7 ke3-chhek koh khah boe7 kiaN5--tit, kiaN-liau2 se3-kan lang5 thiaN-kiN3 an2-ni it-hoat kiaN-hiaN5, kiu5 Siong7-te3 lin5-bin2 pi3-iu7. Koh kun7-lai5 Seng3-keng pian3 thoan5 tak8 sou2-chai7, Seng3-keng lai7 beng5-beng5 ki3-chai3 Siong7-te3 lin5-bin2 thiaN3 se3-kan lang5. Koh kong2 Ia5-sou lim5-kau3 se3-kan m7 si7 beh chio ho2 lang5, si7 beh chio u7 choe7 e5 lang5 hoan2-hoe2 koe2-piN3. Chhin-chhiuN7 chit ho7 i3-su3, Seng3-keng choe7-choe7 sou2-chai7 ki3-chai3 chin siong5-se3, kiam2 si7 li2 eng7 ham5-hou5 e5 oe7 sou2 thang jia-iam2--mah?” Kui2-a2 bo5 oe7 thang in3, kin2 the3--khi3. Ong5 mng7, “Bo5 u7 ho2 ke3-chhek thang lai5 hian3--e5-mah?” Cheng3 kui2 cheng7-cheng7, bo5 chit8 e5 kaN2 in3. Theng5--u7-hiah-ku2, hut-jian5 chit8 e5 kui2-chut chau3, kong2, “Goa2 u7 ho2 ke3-chhek.” Ong5 kong2, “Sim2-mih ke3-chhek? Kin2 chau3--lai5.” In3 kong2, “Goa2 beh ka7 kong2, “Siong7-te3 chhe KiaN2 lai5 se3-kan, chit chat su7 chin-chiaN3 u7 iaN2. Ia5-sou thoe3 lang5 si2 siok8 lang5 e5 choe7 iah8 si7 chin--e5. Choe7-jin5 hoan2-hoe2 koe2-piN3, chiu7 thang tit-tioh8 Siong7-te3 chiap-lap8, che iah8 si7 bo5 peh8-chhat8.” Oe7 kong2 be7 liau2, kui2-ong5 toa7 siu7-khi3, tah hong-chi2 hoah kong2, “Chiau3 li2 sou2 kong2, chhin-chhiuN7 ka3-si7 lang5 bat to7-li2, chhoa7 lang5 kau3 Thian-kok, tu2-tu2 kap goa2 e5 chong-chi2 tui3-hoan2, an2-ni boe7 eng7--tit. The3--khi3, m7 chun2 li2 koh kong2.” 
  Kui2-a2 in3-kong2, “Che si7 sun7 chhiu2 khan iuN5 e5 ke3. ChhiaN2 tai7-ong5 soah siu7-khi3, iong5-un2 goa2 kong2 kau3 beng5-pek8.” Kui2-ong5 chun2, kui2-a2 koh kong2, “Goa2 teng2-bin7 sou2 kong2 hiah-e5 long2-chong2 u7 iaN2, tok8-tok8 kui-oa2 Ia5-sou bian2 siuN cha2. Se3-kan e5 hok-khi3 khoai3-lok8, tioh8 kip8-si5 chhut-lat8 hiong2-siu7, theng3-hau7 beh lim5-chiong e5 si5 chiah sin3 to7-li2 iau2 be7 ti5, i2-keng u7 thang hiong2-siu7 se3-kan e5 eng5-hoa5, koh thang tit-tioh8 lai5-se3 e5 heng7-hok, chit-e5 kiam2 m7 si7 siang hang7 ho2--mah?” Cheng3 kui2 thiaN liau2 toa7 chan3-seng5, o-lo2 i e5 ho2 ke3-chhek, kui2-ong5 iah8 lian2 chhiu2 toa7 chhio3. Tui3 an2-ni khoan2-thai7 i choe3 siong7-teng2 kui2-chut. Ong5 sui5-si5 thoan5 beng7 long2-chong2 e5 toa7 sio2 kui2 kiat-tui7 chiaN5 kun5, jip8 hoan7-kan, choan-choan eng7 chit-e5 ke3-chhek in2-iu2 se3-kan lang5. Sou2-i2 hian7-kim lang5 thiaN to7-li2 pang3 choe3 bo5 iau3-kin2, u7 e5 kong2, “Pat8 jit8.” Chit ho7 long2 si7 tiong3 tioh8 Mou5-kui2 e5 ke3-chhek. 
  Bang7--kiN3 e5 lang5 cheng-sin5 toa7 kiaN, pian3-pian3 ka7 i e5 chhin-lang5 peng5-iu2 kong2. Tak8 e5 kong2 in bat ham7-loh8 chit ho7 ke3-chhek e5 tiong-kan, taN i2-au7 beh soe3-ji7 kin2-sin7, toan3-toan3 m7 hou7 Mou5-kui2 tek-seng3. 
  Chit toaN7 sui-jian5 si7 kong2 khi2 bang7 e5 si5 sou2 khoaN3-kiN3 e5 cheng5-heng5, khiok iah8 thang keng2-seng2 se3-kan lang5. Ia5-sou kong2, “Goa2 tai7-seng khi3 thoe3 lin2 pi7-pan7 khia7-khi2 e5 sou2-chai7.” Thang chai se3-kan lang5 ti7 thian-kok ia7 u7 ui7 thang tiam3. M7-ku2 kui2 ong5 oan3-tou3 e5 sim moa2-moa2, chhut-lat8 pho3-hoai7, tek-khak beh ham7-loh8 se3-kan lam5 lu2 ban7 lang5 gin2-a2 jip8 i e5 lo5-bang7, kap i boat8-jit8 saN-kap biat8-bo5 chiah kam-sim. 
  KhoaN3 chheh e5 peng5-iu2! Tioh8 kin2-sin7 m7-thang hou7 mou5-kui2 u7 ki-hoe7 thang jip8. ThiaN to7-li2 e5 si5 chiu7 tioh8 pho7 tiaN7 sim-chi3 te3 Ia5-sou, bian2 siuN7 beh tai7-seng hiong2-siu7 se3-kan kui2 chap8 ni5 e5 eng5-hoa5 hu3-kui3, chiah eng7 tiap8-a2 ku2 e5 hoan2-hoe2 po2 eng2-oan2 e5 hok-khi3, na7 an2-ni beng5-beng5 si7 jip8 ti7 mou5-kui2 ke3-chhek e5 tiong-kan. Chit8 hang7 si7 kou-hu7 Ki-tok kiu3-siok8 e5 un-tian2, koh chit8 hang7 thian-tong5 eng2-oan2 e5 hok-khi3, chit ho7 lang5 bo5 tek-khak u7 hun7. 
  Bo5 Sin5 Hoe7. 
  Se-kok u7 bo5 sin5 hoe7, siong5-siong5 chu7-chip8 choe7-choe7 lang5 ian2-soat, kong2 thiN-toe7 ban7 mih8 long2 si7 tui3 chu7-jian5 e5 li2 siN-chiaN5, bo5 iaN2 u7 sin5 teh koan2-li2 chiah-e5 tai7-chi3. Tak8 pai2 ian2-soat beng5-pek8, ka7 thiaN e5 lang5 kong2, “Na7 u7 bo5 hang5-hok8 goa2 e5 gi7-lun7--e5, thang chiuN7 tai5 pian7-pok.” U7 chit8 jit8 ian2 soah iu5-goan5 an2-ni kong2, hut-jian5 chit8 e5 lau7 hu7-jin5-lang5 thuh koaiN2-a2 chin3-cheng5 kong2, “Liat8-ui7 sian-siN tu2-a2 sou2 ian2--e5, phah-sng3 bo5 lang5 thang kap lin2 pian7-pok, chiau3 goa2 thiaN liau2 lin2 sou2 gi7-lun7 bo5 tek-khak chun2. Chap8 goa7 ni5 cheng5 goa2 e5 tiong7-hu ke3-si3, lau5 goa2 kap kiaN2-ji5 chit8 ke poeh e5 thau5-chhui3, saN tng3 kou3 long2 boe7 kia7, ke-lai7 khang so-so, chi2 u7 chit8 pho7 Sin ku7 iok Seng3-keng na7-tiaN7. Chit ho7 khou2-keng2 sit8-chai7 si7 kou-ji5 koaN2-hu7 sou2 tong3 boe7-tiau5--e5, chong2-si7 Seng3-keng beng5-beng5 kong2, Siong7-te3 thiaN3 lan2, tui3 an2-ni sim-lai7 tit-tioh8 an-ui3 kou2-bu2 cheng-sin5, oa2-kho3 chap8 ki chng2-thau5-a2 than3 chiah8, ka3-si7 hau7-siN cha-bou2 kiaN2 kau3 chiaN5 lang5, sou2-i2 u7 thang kau3 kin-a2-jit8, long2 si7 Siong7-te3 e5 to7-li2 ka3-si7--goa2, chiu7-si7 Siong7-te3 e5 un-tian2 koan3-kou3 goa2 e5 ian5-kou3. Chap8 goa7 ni5-lai5 kiam5 sng khou2 chiaN2, in-ui7 tioh8-boa5 ke3 thau5 ti3-piN7, khui3-lat8 soe-the3, chai tiam3 se3-kan bo5 ku2, chong2-si7 sim-lai7 peng5-peng5 an-an, tit-tioh8 to7-li2 e5 chin khoai3-lok8, chheng-song2 e5 cheng5, boe7 hiau2 tit eng7 oe7 heng5-iong5 ka7 lang5 kong2, che long2 si7 tui3 Seng3-keng e5 to7-li2 lai5. TaN liat8-ui7 sou2 chhiong3 bo5 sin5 e5 seh, be7 chai ti7 se3-kai3 e5 lang5 u7 siaN2 kam2-eng3? Koh be7 chai ti7 liat8-ui7 u7 siaN2 heng7-hok? ChhiaN2 beng5-beng5 ka7 goa2 kong2.” Tai5 teng2 e5 lang5 kong2, “Lau7 m2 oe7 ti7 Seng3-keng e5 tiong-kan tit-tioh8 chin e5 khoai3-lok8, chai thian-beng7 siu2 song3-hiong, sim moa2 i3-chiok, put-chi2 thang hoaN-hi2 thang o-lo2, chong2-si7 goan2 m7 ai3 kap lau