  Eng-kok chhut mia5 e5 phok-su7 Ou5 Bit8, peng5-seng bo5 tui3-tiong7 chong-kau3. I e5 lau7-bu2 soe3-han3 e5 si5 sin3 to7-li2 put-chi2 chhim, au7--lai5 in-ui7 kiaN2 khah chun-kui3, chiam7-chiam7 hou7 sia7-hoe7 chun-keng3, than3 to7-li2 e5 sim tui3 an2-ni khah leng2-tam7. Beh lim5-chiong e5 si5 kia3 phoe hou7 i e5 kiaN2, tai7-khai3 kong2, “Goa2 taN piN7 tang7, siN3-mia7 chai7 ti7 e7-hng cha2-khi2, chai tek-khak bo5 thang koh tiam3 se3-kan ku2-ku2, ng3-bang7 li2 koaN2-kin2 to3-lai5 hou7 goa2 khoaN3-khoaN3. Li2 u7 chhim e5 hak8-bun7 ti3-sek e5 li2, thang ti7 kan-khou2 e5 si5 an-ui3--goa2, che sin-khu e5 kan-khou2 sng3-si7 sio2-khoa2, tok8-tok8 goa2 sim-lai7 siong5-siong5 siuN7 thau5-cheng5 e5 lou7 bong5-bong5 biau2-biau2 ou-ou am3-am3, hou7 goa2 put-chi2 kiaN-hiaN5. Li2 sou2 chhiong3 e5 hak8-soat, kau3 chit si5 ti7 goa2 choan5 bo5 li7-ek. Siat-su2 li2 boe7 oe7 chhin-sin to3--lai5, iah8 tioh8 kin2-kin2 sia2 phoe lai5 ka7 goa2 kong2, tau3-ti2 u7 siaN2 hoat-tou7 thang an-ui3 goa2 e5 sim. KiaN2 ah! Li2 gou7 goa2! ChaiN2-iuN7 long2 bong5-bang7?” 
  KhoaN3 Ou5 Bit8 e5 lau7-bu2 chai ti7 beh si2 e5 si5 chi2 u7 ng3-bang7 Seng3-to7 an-ui3 i e5 sim, bo5, chiu7 hoan5-lo2 kan-khou2 kau3 boe7 kong2-tit. I lim5-chiong e5 oe7 kau3 hiah pek-chhiat, kau3-giah8 choe3 se3-kan lang5 e5 kam3-kai3, lan2 kiam2 m7 tioh8 liong7 cha2 pi7-pan7--mah? 
  Bat thiaN-kiN3 lang5 kong2, thian-tong5 te7-gek8 si7 ka2-siat e5 oe7, kou2-cha2 lang5 eng7 che lai5 keng2-seng2 se3-kan lang5, m7 si7 sit8-sit8 u7 hit ho7 iaN2-chiah. Chit ku3 sit8-chai7 m7 si7 an2-ni, im-iong5 saN kau-kai3 si7 kek8 kun7, saN thong e5 si5 kek8 khoai3 kau3. Po2-lo5 kong2, “Chit si5 chhin-chhiuN7 kiaN3 lai7 khoaN3 lang5, boe7 bian2 tit hou5-hun7, pat8 jit8 chiu7 kiN3 bin7 tui3 siong3 chin beng5.” Chiu7-si7 chit-e5 i3-su3. Se3-kan chhang-mia5 ti3-sek e5 lang5, kou3-chip ka-ki7 e5 i3-kian3, m7-kheng2 khiam-hu sim soe3-ji7 chha5-kho2, ti3-kau3 sit-loh8 eng2-oah8 e5 hok-khi3, che kiam2 m7 si7 hou7 chhang-mia5 sou2 gou7--mah? 
  Siong7-te3 tiau5-ti5 kang3 Kiu3-se3 Chu2 thoe3 lang5 siok8 choe7, chit-e5 si7 kek8 toa7 e5 chu5-pi, u7 lang5 soah kong2, “Si7 cho7 but8--e5 to su7. Sian7 iu2 sian7 po3, ok iu2 ok po3, si7 chu7-jian5 e5 li2, mih-sai2 eng7 bo5 choe7 lai5 thoe3 u7 choe7, hoan2-tng2 hou7 lang5 khoaN3 choe3 bo5 kong-to7.” Ki5-sit8 m7 si7 bo5 kong-to7, chiaN3-chiaN3 hian2-beng5 thiN-pe7 e5 bo5 han7-liong7. In-ui7 na7 bo5 an2-ni chiu7 se3-kan lang5 long2 tioh8 biat8-bo5. Siong7-te3 e5 sim boe7 jim2 tit cheng3 lang5 tim5-lun5, put-tek-i2 chiah choe3 an2-ni, lang5 put-ko3 tioh8 sun7 siu7. Na7 si7 ka-ki7 ngi7 e5 sim, chiu7-si7 khoaN3-khin teng2-bin7 tek8 piat e5 un, choe7 it-hoat tang7. Goan7 se3-kan lang5 kin2-kin2 chhiN2-gou7. 
